# Plot runs required (convergence difficulty)
plt.scatter(df["carrier-distance"], df["final-runs-used"])
plt.xlabel("Carrier Distance")
plt.ylabel("Runs to Converge")
plt.title("Convergence Difficulty by Scenario")
plt.show()
```

